column2: SELECT N.objID AS objID_gal, GT.ra AS ra_gal, GT.dec AS dec_gal, PZ.z AS z_gal, PZ.zErr AS zErr_gal, HS.RA_DEG_J2# AS ra_qso, HS.DEC_DEG_J2# AS dec_qso, HS.NVSS_RM AS RM_qso, HS.NVSS_RM_ERR AS RMErr_qso, HS.SELECTED_REDSHIFT AS z_qso, HS.SELECTED_REDSHIFT_ERR AS zErr_qso INTO myDB.startfromquasar FROM myDB.Hammond_Short HS CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq (HS.RA_DEG_J2#, HS.DEC_DEG_J2#, #) as N JOIN DR1#.PhotoZ PZ ON N.objID = PZ.objID JOIN DR1#.GalaxyTag GT ON N.objID = GT.objID WHERE PZ.z ! = # AND PZ.zErr ! = # AND PZ.z > = #
